<h1>Augmented Reality</h1>
<h2>Summary</h2>
<p>
  In this project I set out to develop an application that demonstrates augmented reality in a useful setting. Specifically, 
  I experimented with the augmented reality platform <a href="https://developer.apple.com/augmented-reality/">ARKit</a> to develop
  an iOS application that virtually renders wall stud locations in my apartment. I've split the project into three categories – 
  <a href="/ar_tools">Toolkit</a>, <a href="/ar_models">Models</a> and <a href="/ar_inter">Interaction</a> – where each category
  is used to illustrate my first development experience in the world of augmented reality.
</p>
